data.description: SADDLE UP!! LIVE THE LIFE YOU LOVE....Lots of Room to Roam on this 5+/- farmette....Inviting, spacious farmhouse with a laid back vibe surrounded by wide open space and fresh air, this lovely home features 4 comfortable size bedrooms & 2.5 baths (primary bedroom with 2 walk-in closets, bathroom with double vanity, double headed shower), charming large country kitchen with island and breakfast area,  beautiful family room with cathedral ceiling, fireplace and tons of natural light, formal dining room and living room and/or office area.  Additional highlights of this home include, full unfinished walk-out basement, back deck overlooking the pasture, front porch, hardwood & engineered wood floors, dual zoned HVAC and 2 car attached garage.  The exterior of the property includes 4 stall barn with electric, hot & cold water, 1 wash stall, hay loft, tack room with sink and approximately 4 fenced-in acres.  Conveniently located to Bay Bridge and Delaware
